window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The extraordinary manifesto of independent living - newly abridged and introduced in this powerful condensation</b> </p> <p><i>Self-Reliance</i> is a life-changing experience - its message of nonconformity, self-expression, and personal independence can awaken you to a new, and better, way of living. Now, historian and New Thought scholar Mitch Horowitz has deftly and faithfully retained the most powerful ideas of Ralph Waldo Emerson's original classic, and reintroduced this work in this one-of-a-kind condensation. Listenable within the space of an average commute or lunch hour, the experience of <i>Self-Reliance</i> may represent a true turning point in your life. </p>"; 
